==Standings==
{{2026 FIFA World Cup group tables|Group F}}

In the [[2026 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Round of 32|round of 32]]:<ref name="regulations"/>
* The winner of Group F will advance to play the runner-up of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group C|Group C]].
* The runner-up of Group F will advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group C|Group C]].
* The third-placed team of Group F might advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group A|Group A]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group B|Group B]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group D|Group D]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group E|Group E]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group I|Group I]] (if one of the [[2026 FIFA World Cup#Ranking of third-placed teams|eight best third-placed teams]] from the group stage).

==Matches==
All times listed are local.<ref name="match schedule"/>

===Netherlands vs Japan===
The teams have met three times prior, including the Netherlands' [[2010 FIFA World Cup Group E#Netherlands vs Japan|1–0 group stage victory]] at the [[2010 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Netherlands vs. Japan Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/holland_vs_japan.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=5 December 2025}}</ref> Their most recent meeting took place in 2013, a 2–2 friendly draw.<ref>{{cite web|title=Netherlands national football team: record v Japan|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/netherlands/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Japan|website=11v11.com|access-date=5 December 2025}}</ref>

