===Tunisia vs Japan===
The teams have previously met six times, including Japan's [[2002 FIFA World Cup Group H#Tunisia vs Japan|2–0 group stage victory]] at the [[2002 FIFA World Cup]] (which they co-hosted with South Korea). Their latest meeting took place in the 2023 Kirin Challenge Cup, which Japan also won by 2–0.<ref>{{cite web|title=Tunisia national football team: record v Japan|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/tunisia/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Japan|website=11v11.com|access-date=5 December 2025}}</ref> This will be the 1000th World Cup match.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/story/_/id/47224100/fifa-2026-world-cup-match-schedule-final-kickoff-usa|title=2026 World Cup schedule: FIFA reveals match times, locations|work=ESPN|access-date=7 December 2025}}</ref>

